"Show the consent banner and block configured scripts/iframes until the "
"visitor agrees"
msgstr ""
"Afficher la bannière de consentement et bloquer les scripts/iframes "
"configurés jusqu’à ce que le visiteur accepte"

#: views/admin-settings.php:100
msgid ""
"The banner only appears once you have added at least one block rule or "
"inline script (Blocking tab)."
msgstr ""
"La bannière n’apparaît qu’une fois que vous avez ajouté au moins une règle "
"de blocage ou un script inline (onglet Blocage)."

#: views/admin-settings.php:102
msgid "Consent model"
msgstr "Modèle de consentement"

#: views/admin-settings.php:103
msgid "Opt-in (EU / GDPR)"
msgstr "Opt-in (UE / RGPD)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:104
msgid "Opt-in only in v1: nothing optional loads until the visitor agrees."
msgstr ""
"Opt-in uniquement en v1 : aucun élément optionnel ne se charge tant que le "
"visiteur n’a pas accepté."

#: views/admin-settings.php:106
msgid "Remember a choice for (days)"
msgstr "Mémoriser un choix pendant (jours)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:106
msgid ""
"How long the visitor’s decision is remembered before the banner asks again — "
"the consent cookie and the proof’s renewal date follow these (separate from "
"the proof log’s retention). As of July 2026, the CNIL advises keeping a "
"refusal for at least 6 months (180 days)."
msgstr ""
"Durée pendant laquelle la décision du visiteur est mémorisée avant que la "
"bannière redemande — le cookie de consentement et la date de renouvellement "
"de la preuve suivent ces valeurs (distinct de la conservation du journal de "
"preuves). Depuis juillet 2026, la CNIL recommande de conserver un refus "
"pendant au moins 6 mois (180 jours)."

#: views/admin-settings.php:108
msgid "After accepting"
msgstr "Après acceptation"

#: views/admin-settings.php:110
msgid "After refusing"
msgstr "Après refus"

#: views/admin-settings.php:114
msgid "Show to logged-in users"
msgstr "Afficher aux utilisateurs connectés"

#: views/admin-settings.php:115
msgid ""
"Run consent + blocking for logged-in users too (off = logged-in users see "
"the unmodified site)"
msgstr ""
"Appliquer le consentement et le blocage aussi aux utilisateurs connectés "
"(désactivé = les utilisateurs connectés voient le site non modifié)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:117
msgid "Respect DNT / GPC"
msgstr "Respecter DNT / GPC"

#: views/admin-settings.php:118
msgid ""
"Treat a Do-Not-Track / Global-Privacy-Control browser signal as a refusal of "
"optional cookies"
msgstr ""
"Traiter un signal de navigateur Do-Not-Track / Global-Privacy-Control comme "
"un refus des cookies optionnels"

#: views/admin-settings.php:119
msgid "…and hide the banner entirely for those visitors (otherwise still ask)"
msgstr ""
"…et masquer entièrement la bannière pour ces visiteurs (sinon, demander "
"quand même)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:122
msgid "Proof of consent"
msgstr "Preuve de consentement"

#: views/admin-settings.php:124
msgid "Store proof of consent"
msgstr "Stocker la preuve de consentement"

#: views/admin-settings.php:125
msgid ""
"Record each consent decision in the database (advised for GDPR "
"accountability)"
msgstr ""
"Enregistrer chaque décision de consentement dans la base de données "
"(conseillé pour la responsabilité RGPD)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:127
msgid "IP address"
msgstr "Adresse IP"

#: views/admin-settings.php:127
msgid ""
"A salted hash is irreversible but still lets you count unique consents. Your "
"server already logs IPs; GDPR requires disclosing it, not omitting it."
msgstr ""
"Un hachage salé est irréversible tout en vous permettant de comptabiliser "
"les consentements uniques. Votre serveur enregistre déjà les IP ; le RGPD "
"exige de le divulguer, pas de l’omettre."

#: views/admin-settings.php:129
msgid "Store a salted hash (recommended)"
msgstr "Stocker un hachage salé (recommandé)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:129
msgid "Store the full IP"
msgstr "Stocker l’IP complète"

#: views/admin-settings.php:133
msgid "Store user-agent"
msgstr "Stocker le user-agent"

#: views/admin-settings.php:134
msgid "Record the browser user-agent string"
msgstr "Enregistrer la chaîne user-agent du navigateur"

#: views/admin-settings.php:136
msgid "Store WP user"
msgstr "Stocker l’utilisateur WP"

#: views/admin-settings.php:137
msgid "Record the logged-in user (guests are never identified)"
msgstr ""
"Enregistrer l’utilisateur connecté (les invités ne sont jamais identifiés)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:139
msgid "Log retention (days)"
msgstr "Conservation du journal (jours)"

#: views/admin-settings.php:140 views/admin-settings.php:271
#: views/admin-settings.php:367 views/admin-settings.php:371
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Par défaut"

#: views/admin-settings.php:140
msgid "0 = keep forever"
msgstr "0 = conserver indéfiniment"

#: views/admin-settings.php:141
msgid ""
"Proof of consent should be kept at least as long as the consent lasts (the "
"consent duration above) — otherwise you may delete evidence for consents "
"that are still valid."
msgstr ""
"La preuve de consentement doit être conservée au moins aussi longtemps que "
"le consentement (la durée de consentement ci-dessus) — sinon vous risquez de "
"supprimer des preuves pour des consentements encore valides."

#: views/admin-settings.php:143
msgid "On uninstall"
msgstr "À la désinstallation"

#: views/admin-settings.php:143
msgid ""
"Deleting the plugin normally removes everything, including the consent log. "
"Keep it if you may need the proof of consent after uninstalling (legal "
"accountability) — re-installing later will reuse it."
msgstr ""
"Supprimer l’extension efface normalement tout, y compris le journal de "
"consentement. Conservez-le si vous pourriez avoir besoin de la preuve de "
"consentement après la désinstallation (responsabilité légale) — une "
"réinstallation ultérieure le réutilisera."

#: views/admin-settings.php:144
msgid "Keep the consent log (proof of consent) when uninstalling"
msgstr ""
"Conserver le journal de consentement (preuve de consentement) à la "
"désinstallation"

#: views/admin-settings.php:152 views/admin-settings.php:314
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Texte"

#: views/admin-settings.php:153
msgid "Presets"
msgstr "Préréglages"

#: views/admin-settings.php:161 views/admin-settings.php:669
msgid "Header"
msgstr "En-tête"

#: views/admin-settings.php:163 views/admin-settings.php:670
msgid "Message"
msgstr "Message"

#: views/admin-settings.php:165
msgid "Accept button"
msgstr "Bouton Accepter"

#: views/admin-settings.php:165
msgid ""
"The one-click “accept everything” button. If you hide it, visitors give "
"consent via Customize → Save instead."
msgstr ""
"Le bouton « tout accepter » en un clic. Si vous le masquez, les visiteurs "
"donnent leur consentement via Personnaliser → Enregistrer."

#: views/admin-settings.php:166 views/admin-settings.php:169
#: views/admin-settings.php:186 views/admin-settings.php:189
msgid "Show"
msgstr "Afficher"

#: views/admin-settings.php:168
msgid "Deny button"
msgstr "Bouton Refuser"

#: views/admin-settings.php:168
msgid ""
"Refuses every optional category, keeping only strictly-necessary "
"(functional) cookies. If something is genuinely required — a CAPTCHA, a "
"payment script — list it under the functional category so it is referenced "
"but never blocked."
msgstr ""
"Refuse toutes les catégories optionnelles et ne conserve que les cookies "
"strictement nécessaires (fonctionnels). Si un élément est réellement "
"indispensable — un CAPTCHA, un script de paiement — placez-le dans la "
"catégorie fonctionnelle : il sera référencé mais jamais bloqué."

#: views/admin-settings.php:171
msgid "Refuse style"
msgstr "Style du refus"

#: views/admin-settings.php:171
msgid ""
"Show refusal as a normal button, or as a subtle “Continue without accepting” "
"link (same effect as closing the banner). A link nudges toward acceptance — "
"note that GDPR/CNIL expect refusing to be as easy as accepting."
msgstr ""
"Afficher le refus sous forme de bouton classique ou de lien discret "
"« Continuer sans accepter » (même effet que fermer la bannière). Un lien "
"incite à accepter — notez que le RGPD/la CNIL attendent qu’il soit aussi "
"simple de refuser que d’accepter."

#: views/admin-settings.php:173
